CM Variable-length half-wave dipole template
CM
CM Use with --vars to substitute HALF_LENGTH_M and FREQ_MHZ at run time.
CM Example:
CM   fnec --vars corpus/dipole-vars.toml corpus/variable-dipole.nec
CM
CM Variables:
CM   HALF_LENGTH_M  — half-length of dipole arm in metres (e.g. 5.282 for 14.2 MHz)
CM   FREQ_MHZ       — excitation frequency in MHz
CE
GW 1 51 0 0 -$HALF_LENGTH_M 0 0 $HALF_LENGTH_M 0.001
GE
EX 0 1 26 0 1.0 0.0
FR 0 1 0 0 $FREQ_MHZ 0.0
EN
